<h2 id="display-campaign-overview">5. Displaying the campaign overview</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>Orders » Coupons</strong> menu in the tab <strong>Campaigns</strong>, the most important information about the created campaigns are displayed in the overview. <a href="#table-campaign-overview">Table 5</a> explains the campaign overview. Use the function <strong>Customise layout</strong> and decide which information should be displayed in the overview. This function is only visible when you point with the mouse over the title bar in the overview.</p>
</div>
