<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="coupon-total-invoice">9.6. Displaying the coupon total on invoices</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Each coupon that is sold is displayed as an individual variation on the invoice. To display the sum of redeemed vouchers on invoices, a name has to be entered in the <strong>Coupon amount</strong> field in the layout of the <a href="/en/orders/order-documents/generating-invoices">invoice</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
